question: Which frequent flyers have the same first name but different last names?
query:
SELECT DISTINCT ff1.frequent_flyer_id, ff1.first_name, ff1.last_name, ff1.card_num, ff1.level, ff1.award_points, ff1.email, ff1.phone, ff1.update_ts
FROM postgres_air.frequent_flyer ff1
JOIN postgres_air.frequent_flyer ff2 ON ff1.first_name = ff2.first_name AND ff1.last_name <> ff2.last_name
ORDER BY ff1.first_name, ff1.last_name;
